  <div data-component="article-content">


            <p>It looks like <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/movies/the-super-mario-galaxy-movie-2026">The Super Mario Galaxy Movie</a>'s home theatre debut may be coming a little later than first reported.</p>
<p>Though the movie <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/super-mario-galaxy-movie-digital-home-release-date-rumour">had been expected to launch on digital and VOD platforms tomorrow, 5th May</a>, <a href="https://whentostream.com/the-super-mario-galaxy-movie-digital-streaming-release-date-revealed/">When to Stream</a> has now updated its original release schedule, pushing this back a couple of weeks to 19th May.</p>
<figure>
<p>
